OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,FBlackburn Rovers have led the tributes
OL,7,Fto club legend Tony Parkes, who has
OL,8,Fdied at the age of 76.
OL,10,FKnown affectionately as 'Mr Blackburn
OL,11,FRovers', he dedicated more than three
OL,12,Fdecades of his life to the Ewood Park
OL,13,Fclub as a player, coach, and manager.
OL,15,FThe Lancashire club said they are
OL,16,F"devastated" by the loss of one of
OL,17,Ftheir most well known players, who had
OL,18,Fbeen living with Alzheimer's disease.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
