CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,FTony arrived at Blackburn in May 1970
OL,7,Ffrom non-league Buxton Town for a
OL,8,Fmodest fee of just #5,000 but it
OL,9,Fproved to be one of the greatest
OL,10,Finvestments in the club's 150-year
OL,11,Fhistory.
OL,13,FParkes was part of the team which
OL,14,Flifted the Third Division title in
OL,15,F1975 and secured immediate promotion
OL,16,Fback to the second tier following the
OL,17,Fclub's relegation in 1979.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
