PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,FHe made 409 appearances as a player
OL,7,Fbefore hanging up his boots in 1982.
OL,8,FHe went on to become the first-team
OL,9,Fcoach under new manager Bobby Saxton
OL,10,Fand served six spells as caretaker
OL,11,Fmanager.
OL,13,FTony worked under 16 different
OL,14,Fmanagers as a coach, including Kenny
OL,15,FDalglish during the Premiership title-
OL,16,Fwinning season in 1994-95.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
