PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,FHis most memorable time during his
OL,7,Fcaretaker stints came in the 1996-97
OL,8,Fseason following the departure of Ray
OL,9,FHarford when he steered the club away
OL,10,Ffrom relegation danger.
OL,12,FHe left Blackburn in November 2004 and
OL,13,Fwent on to scout for Leicester City
OL,14,Fbefore becoming Simon Grayson's
OL,15,Fassistant at Blackpool, where he
OL,16,Ffinished his coaching career.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
