PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Blackburn Rovers
OL,7,Fsaid: "Everyone at the club sends
OL,8,Ftheir deepest heartfelt condolences to
OL,9,FTony's daughter Natalie and all his
OL,10,Ffamily and friends at this incredibly
OL,11,Fsad time."
OL,13,FFormer Blackburn manager Sir Kenny
OL,14,FDalglish added on X: "Very sad to hear
OL,15,Fabout the passing of Tony Parkes. A
OL,16,Ffantastic man who I had the privilege
OL,17,Fof working alongside at Blackburn.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
