CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777043470
OL,3,CTributes paid to Blackburn legend Tony
OL,4,CParkes
OL,6,F"Loyal, dedicated and someone who gave
OL,7,Feverything to the club. My thoughts
OL,8,Fare with his family and everyone
OL,9,Fconnected with Blackburn Rovers."
OL,11,FThe club is inviting supporters to lay
OL,12,Fflowers to Tony Parkes at the Jack
OL,13,FWalker statue at Ewood Park and have
OL,14,Fopened a book of condolences at the
OL,15,FBlackburn End reception.
OL,17,FA special tribute to celebrate Tony's
OL,18,Flife and his extraordinary
OL,19,Fcontribution to Rovers' history will
OL,20,Fbe held during the final home game of
OL,21,Fthe season.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]
